# 📊 KPI Dashboard for Business & Contract Performance

## 🧠 Problem Statement
Tracking contract performance and SLAs manually leads to inefficiencies and delayed decision-making.  
This project builds a **KPI dashboard system** for monitoring performance in real-time.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Excel (Advanced)
- Tableau (Dashboard Visualization)
- Data Analysis

